enb_long_title: Twenty-sixth sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies (SB 26) of the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC)
section_title: ANALYSIS OF MITIGATION POTENTIALS AND REVIEW OF WORK PROGRAMME:
sentences: AWG Chair Charles introduced the agenda item on mitigation potentials and ranges of Annex I emissions objectives, and the item on the work programme and schedule of future sessions.
He proposed, and parties agreed to, a contact group that would start work on Wednesday at 1:30 pm.
